description:
Makin Tracks e03

Jerry is thrilled with Katie's progress, and initiates her into the Campbell clan by giving her a six-shooter bearing the family crest. Katie takes the gesture a little too literally: she goes to shoot a hog surrounded by dogs. 


Real Texas Hero e04

Jerry lands a job of a lifetime: cleaning hogs off the ranch of Dean Smith, an Olympic medalist and former stunt double for John Wayne. Jerry takes this work for a "real Texas hero with a real Texas hog problem" very seriously.
